criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          1. Residents aged 30 to 79, whose residence is consistent with their registered permanent
             residence location;

          2. Residents who voluntarily participate in the project, agree to the collection of their
             biological information, and sign the informed consent form;

          3. Residents who have no mental illness and other related diseases, and display a normal
             ability of expression and understanding;

        Exclusion Criteria:

          1. Residents who reject collaboration;

          2. Residents who allow no follow-up visits.
